lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_SHERIFF_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Sheriff Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Gunslinging and Prospecting skills!\n\nIt's as if you're a sheriff, patrolling the west and getting gold!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_GI_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' G.I. Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Commando and Sneaking skills!\n\nIt's as if you're a G.I., sneaking through the jungle and firing on enemies!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_SNIPER_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Sniper Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Rifleman and Outdoorsman skills!\n\nIt's as if you're a sniper, lining up your shot and living off the land!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_PROFESSOR_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Professor Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Energy Weapon and Science skills!\n\nIt's as if you're a mad professor, making new lasers and firing them at unsuspecting victims!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_BRAWLER_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Brawler Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Melee Weapon and Unarmed skills!\n\nIt's as if you're a brawler, smashing your opponents with both mace and face!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_SCHMOOZER_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Schmoozer Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Barter and Speech skills!\n\nIt's as if you're a real schmoozer, haggling prices and changing minds!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_TINKERER_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Tinkerer Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Engineer and Explosive skills!\n\nIt’s as if you’re a tinkerer, making niche gadgets and blowing them up!"
lang["#MOD_SKILL_CLOTH_DOCTOR_DESC"] = "The Vault-Tec Lil' Brawler Clothskill Module is guaranteed to improve the wearer's Medical skills!\n\nYou're a surgeon, Dr. Han!\nA real surgeon!"

